15
00:00:39,230 --> 00:00:41,690
At least two Americans tied to the US consulate

16
00:00:41,690 --> 00:00:44,320
in the southern Chinese city of Guangzhou

17
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:47,350
have been evacuated due to mysterious ailments

18
00:00:47,350 --> 00:00:51,040
that came after they heard odd sounds.

19
00:00:51,040 --> 00:00:54,400
A US State Department Spokeswoman said Wednesday
night

20
00:00:54,410 --> 00:00:57,240
that the Department has sent a number of individuals

21
00:00:57,250 --> 00:01:00,250
for further evaluation in the United States.

22
00:01:00,250 --> 00:01:02,530
A US official spoke to ABC news,

23
00:01:02,530 --> 00:01:04,600
saying the evacuated Americans were,

24
00:01:04,600 --> 00:01:08,340
“being brought for testing to the University
of Pennsylvania.”

25
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:11,700
It follows this health advisory from the US
embassy in China,

26
00:01:11,700 --> 00:01:15,550
warning that, “If you experience any unusual
acute auditory

27
00:01:15,550 --> 00:01:17,990
or sensory phenomena accompanied by

28
00:01:17,990 --> 00:01:21,040
unusual sounds or piercing noises,

29
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:23,000
do not attempt to locate their source.

30
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,610
Instead, move to a location

31
00:01:24,610 --> 00:01:27,500
where the sounds are not present.”

32
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:30,549
Which seems like the plot to a bad 1950’s
B-movie.

33
00:01:30,549 --> 00:01:32,979
“The Sound from Space.”

34
00:01:32,979 --> 00:01:34,920
One US consulate employee was diagnosed

35
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:38,140
with a “mild traumatic brain injury.”

36
00:01:38,140 --> 00:01:41,659
And that followed a similar incident last
year in Havana, Cuba.

37
00:01:41,659 --> 00:01:44,530
24 US Embassy employees reported symptoms

38
00:01:44,530 --> 00:01:48,920
similar to a concussion after, “some sort
of ‘acoustic element,’

39
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,979
such as a ‘high-pitched beam of sound’

40
00:01:50,979 --> 00:01:53,560
or a ‘baffling sensation akin to driving

41
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,880
