42
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:56,880
“US believes that several state department
employees

43
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:57,880
at US embassy in Havana,

44
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:58,880
have been have been subjected to acoustic
attack?

45
00:01:58,880 --> 00:01:59,880
What does that even mean?”

46
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,880
That’s exactly how my college girlfriend
reacted

47
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:01,880
when I told her I was starting a baroque metal
band

48
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:03,180
called Acoustic Attack.

49
00:02:03,180 --> 00:02:04,830
Back to China.

50
00:02:04,830 --> 00:02:06,470
The New York Times uncovered the identity

51
00:02:06,470 --> 00:02:08,819
of one of the two most recent evacuees

52
00:02:08,819 --> 00:02:11,260
from the US consulate in Guangzhou.

53
00:02:11,260 --> 00:02:12,260
And apparently,

54
00:02:12,260 --> 00:02:15,230
he had complained in an email to the entire
consulate

55
00:02:15,230 --> 00:02:19,099
that they were lied to about how serious the
situation was.

56
00:02:19,099 --> 00:02:20,540
That’s why he and his wife

57
00:02:20,540 --> 00:02:23,690
didn’t report their symptoms right away.

58
00:02:23,690 --> 00:02:25,310
His symptoms included “dizziness,

59
00:02:25,310 --> 00:02:27,770
headaches and an inability to concentrate.”

60
00:02:27,770 --> 00:02:31,680
Wait, that just sounds like a normal day at
the office.

61
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:33,120
But in all these cases,

62
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:35,500
victims report hearing a strange sound

63
00:02:35,500 --> 00:02:38,010
before suffering physical symptoms.

64
00:02:38,010 --> 00:02:40,370
No one knows for sure what’s behind it.

65
00:02:40,370 --> 00:02:42,590
One explanation is it’s a sonic attack.

66
00:02:42,590 --> 00:02:44,459
I know what you’re thinking,

67
00:02:44,459 --> 00:02:47,320
I haven’t had a sonic attack since 1991.

68
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:50,570
Yeah, the original game was from 1991.

69
00:02:50,570 --> 00:02:51,660
You are old.

70
00:02:51,660 --> 00:02:55,630
But weaponizing frequencies is very real technology,

71
00:02:55,630 --> 00:02:59,069
not just some crazy scheme by Dr. Robotnik.

72
00:02:59,069 --> 00:03:01,600
There are three types of sonic weapons.

73
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:02,930
The first type is simply playing

74
00:03:02,930 --> 00:03:05,740
music or sound really, really loud.

75
00:03:05,740 --> 00:03:07,180
Like a Limp Bizkit concert.

76
00:03:07,180 --> 00:03:10,230
Now that’s a sonic attack.

77
00:03:10,230 --> 00:03:11,569
Another type of sonic weapon

78
00:03:11,569 --> 00:03:14,450
is called an infrasonic weapon.

79
00:03:14,450 --> 00:03:16,810
It blasts loud, low frequency sounds

80
00:03:16,810 --> 00:03:19,069
that can’t be heard by the human ear,

81
00:03:19,069 --> 00:03:20,700
but can be felt.

82
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:22,261
This technology has been used to,

83
00:03:22,261 --> 00:03:24,319
I kid you not,

84
00:03:24,319 --> 00:03:26,190
fight off pirates.

85
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:27,450
And everyone knows that pirates

86
00:03:27,450 --> 00:03:30,030
are just like diplomats.

87
00:03:30,030 --> 00:03:32,849
But it’s unlikely infrasonic weapons are
the culprit.

88
00:03:32,849 --> 00:03:35,319
They’re typically pretty bulky—

89
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:37,739
not something you can hide in a consulate.

90
00:03:37,739 --> 00:03:40,220
The effects include excruciating headaches,

91
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:43,620
ear pain, and even involuntary defecation.

92
00:03:43,620 --> 00:03:47,349
That’s not what the consulate employees
reported.

93
00:03:47,349 --> 00:03:48,480
But then again,

94
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:53,020
would you tell your boss if you had involuntary
defecation?

95
00:03:53,020 --> 00:03:56,530
The third type of sonic weapon is ultrasonic
weapons.

96
00:03:56,530 --> 00:03:59,500
Those are frequencies too high to hear.

97
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:01,850
They can cause nausea and headaches—

98
00:04:01,850 --> 00:04:06,650
which is like the symptoms the US diplomats
suffered from.

99
00:04:06,650 --> 00:04:09,409
But there are problems with this theory.

100
00:04:09,409 --> 00:04:11,819
Ultrasonic emitters are very short range.

101
00:04:11,819 --> 00:04:14,569
Like, if you’re standing on the other side
of the room,

102
00:04:14,569 --> 00:04:15,769
that’s too far,

103
00:04:15,769 --> 00:04:17,980
kind of short range.

104
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:19,410
Then there’s the fact that,

105
00:04:19,410 --> 00:04:22,140
“Ultrasound is also highly directional.

106
00:04:22,140 --> 00:04:25,120
Precise alignment in millimetres would be
needed to steer

107
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:28,310
an ultrasonic ‘beam’ to hit someone from
across a room.”

108
00:04:28,310 --> 00:04:30,760
It’d be like if Goldfinger said,

109
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:33,660
“I expect you to die, Mr. Bond. J

110
00:04:33,660 --> 00:04:36,060
ust uhh...that bench doesn’t have chains,

111
00:04:36,060 --> 00:04:37,860
so...stay right there.”

112
00:04:37,860 --> 00:04:42,060
OK, so probably not ultrasonic weapons either.

113
00:04:42,060 --> 00:04:44,639
So...are there any other theories?

114
00:04:44,639 --> 00:04:46,660
Yes, actually.

115
00:04:46,660 --> 00:04:48,820
These might not have been ultrasonic weapons,

116
00:04:48,820 --> 00:04:53,440
