117
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:56,840
You see Ultrasound is also used in motion
sensors.

118
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:59,190
And studies have found it can even be used
to read

119
00:04:59,190 --> 00:05:01,530
a person’s mouth in noisy rooms,

120
00:05:01,530 --> 00:05:03,669
